<title>USA: Supreme International oks 3-for-2 split.</title>
<headline>Supreme International oks 3-for-2 split.</headline>
<dateline>MIAMI 1997-07-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Supreme International Corp said Monday its board approved a 3-for-2 stock split.</p>
<p>The split will be in the form of a stock dividend to be distributed on or about August 15 to shareholders of record on July 31.</p>
<p>Shareholders will receive three shares of common stock for every two shares of the company's stock held on the record date.</p>
<p>Supreme International currently has about 4.35 million shares of common stock issued and outstanding.</p>
<p>The company said it is confident it will continue its &quot;record&quot; financial performance during this fiscal year.</p>
</text>
